text: Vytautas Landsbergis-Žemkalnis (b. March 10, 1893 Linkavičiai, Pakruojo valsčius – d. May 21, 1993 Vilnius) was a Lithuanian architect. He was the father of Lithuanian independence fighter and politician Vytautas Landsbergis.Atminimas.kvb.lt: Biography ==References== Category:Lithuanian architects Category:Lithuanian centenarians Category:1893 births Category:1993 deaths Category:20th-century architects
